SELECT ALL AC_GL_NO, AC_GL_DESC, CUST_NAME1 FROM OLTB_ACCOUNT A WHERE (BRANCH_CODE = ? OR (BRANCH_CODE IS NULL AND NVL(BRANCH_CODE, NVL(?, '***')) = NVL(?, '***'))) AND AC_GL_REC_STATUS = 'O' AND (A.AC_OR_GL = 'G' OR (A.AC_OR_GL = 'A' AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM OLVWS_PROD_ACNT_ACCESS X WHERE X.AC_GL_NO = A.AC_GL_NO AND X.PRODUCT_CODE = ?))) ORDER BY AC_GL_NO
SELECT CCY_CODE, CCY_NAME FROM CYTMS_CCY_DEFN WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A'
